#: ../../source/01_installation.rst:177
msgid ""
"**MARC21:** Selected by default, as it is more commonly used globally than "
"UNIMARC."
msgstr "**MARC 21：** 預選的格式，受美國文化影響的地區常使用它。"

#: ../../source/01_installation.rst:179
